title: Vehicle tail light lens

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a vehicle tail light lens, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a frontal perspective view of a left vehicle tail light lens attached to a vehicle, no part of the vehicle is claimed;
FIG. 2 is a left perspective view of the left vehicle tail light lens;
FIG. 3 is a front elevation view of the left vehicle tail light lens;
FIG. 4 is a left side elevation view of the left vehicle tail light lens;
FIG. 5 is a top plan view of the left vehicle tail light lens;
FIG. 6 is a bottom plan view of the left vehicle tail light lens;
FIG. 7 is a right side elevation view of the left vehicle tail light lens;

FIG. 8 is a frontal perspective view of an alternative embodiment of the tailight lens illustrated in FIGS. 1-7, showing a right vehicle tail light lens attached to a vehicle, no part of the vehicle is claimed;
FIG. 9 is a perspective view of the right vehicle tail light lens;
FIG. 10 is a front elevation view of the right vehicle tail light lens;
FIG. 11 is a right side elevation view of the right vehicle tail light lens;
FIG. 12 is a top plan view of the right vehicle tail light lens;
FIG. 13 is a bottom plan view of the right vehicle tail light lens; and,
FIG. 14 is a left side elevation view of the right vehicle tail light lens.
The phantom lines are not a part of the claimed invention.
